1quviasutsiaqpuq ajuqsaqtunik isumagijaqaqtuq;
2ataniup saputisimaniarngmagu uumatinniaqlugulu;
3ataniullu sannginirngmik tunisiviginiaqpaa
4uqalauqpunga, “ataniiq, nikagilaunnga;
5akiraqtuqtima piungittunik uqausiringmanga:
6takujaqtuqtauguma, tavva sulingittunik uqausiqaqpuq;
7uvannik piuksangittut uqapiluqatigiikput pitjutigillunga;
8uqaqlutiglu, “qanimmasirngmununa piungittualungmut pijausimajuq,
9piqannarijamaluunniit qaujimatsiaqtama sulijuritsiaqtamalu,
10ivvilli ataniiq, nikagilaunnga,
11qaujimavungali quviagitsiaravinga,
12uvangali najummivarngma pinasuatsiarngnira pillugu,
13ataniq niqtuqtauli, iisaᕅlitit guutingat,
